[2] Cases in various countries
Caribbean
---
Puero Rico. 4 Jul 2012. The number of detected dengue cases is running at above-average levels as Puerto Rico enters the peak season for the painful disease. The territory's health secretary Lorenzo Gonzalez says 111 cases were reported the 1st week of June and 117 cases the previous week. 8 cases of the more severe hemorrhagic form have been confirmed, though no one has died.
http://www.newser.com/article/d9vq7tbg3/puerto-rico-notes-sharp-increase-in-dengue-cases.html

[A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map showing the location of Puerto Rico in the Caribbean can be accessed at http://healthmap.org/r/2AEl. - Mod.TY]

Latin America
---
- Mexico (Tuxtepec, Oaxaca state) 4 Jul 2012. The Tuxtepec municipal director of health, Dr Gilberto de Jesus Rendon Benitez, said yesterday [3 Jul 2012] that the region has an outbreak of classical dengue fever and DHF outbreak that is a little out of control. He stated that the hospitals are saturated with patients with one or the other types of dengue and the increase continues despite the intensive prevention campaign that has been carried out in the populace for a year.
http://e-oaxaca.com/index.php?option=com_k2&view=item&id=14897:brote-de-dengue-hemorrágico-y-común-fuera-de-control-en-tuxtepec&Itemid=321 in Spanish, transl. Mod.TY.

[A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map showing the location of Tuxtepec in Oaxaca state be accessed at http://healthmap.org/r/2Itu. - Mod.TY]

- Honduras (Choloma, Cortes department) 1 Jun 2012. The [health] authorities issue an alert. From epidemiological weeks 19-24, 9 new cases of DHF have been confirmed in Cortes department [state equivalent], and 7 in Choloma municipality. The patients were attended to in the Social Security and Mario Rivas Hospitals. There are additional cases in Lopez Arellano, Las Americas, Prados I and La Hade
http://www.laprensa.hn/Secciones-Principales/Honduras/Valle-de-Sula/Alarma-por-brote-de-dengue-hemorragico-en-Choloma#.T_kDCK7_scw in Spanish, transl. Mod.TY.

[A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map showing the location of Choloma in Cortes department can be accessed at http://healthmap.org/r/2Ity. - Mod.TY]

- Brazil (Campinas, Sao Paulo state) 20 Jun 2012. Dengue virus type 4 is circulating in Campinas. It was diagnosed in the southeast region that had 397 cases of the disease this year [2012], or 67 per cent of the total of 694 confirmed cases in the 1st 5 months of this year [2012]. According to Health Surveillance this is the 1st time that this virus type has circulated in Campinas since the introduction of _Aedes aegypti_ in the decade of the 1990s.
http://www.band.com.br/noticias/cidades/noticia/?id=100000511579 in Portuguese, transl. Mod.TY.

[A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map showing the location of Campinas, Sao Paulo state, can be accessed at http://healthmap.org/r/0Eix. - Mod.TY]

- Brazil (Sao Paulo state interior) 29 Jun 2012. Dengue cases increase in the region. In other cities in the interior of Sao Paulo state, the situation is also getting attention. In Aracatuba there are 1136 cases confirmed by the state Secretariat of Health, in Bauru, 24; Marilia, 36; and in Rio Preto through the month of June there are 280 cases and one death.
http://www.band.com.br/tv/spinterior/noticias.asp?id=100000513584 in Portuguese, transl. Mod.TY.

[A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map showing the location of Sap Paulo state can be accessed at http://healthmap.org/r/0083. - Mod.TY]

- Brazil (Santos, Sao Paulo state) 3 Jul 2012. This year [2012] up to 28 Jun, there were 334 dengue cases, 329 of which were classical dengue fever, 4 dengue with complications, and one DHF case.
http://www.band.com.br/noticias/cidades/noticia/?id=100000514425 in Portuguese, transl. Mod.TY.

[A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map showing the location of Santos, Sao Paulo state, can be accessed at http://healthmap.org/r/2Itw. - Mod.TY]

Asia
---
- India (Thiruvanathapuram, Kerala state) 4 Jul 2012. Nemom block in the district has become the most sensitive region for dengue fever. Out of the 957 cases reported from the district, 300 cases are from the regions coming under this block.
http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-07-04/thiruvananthapuram/32536572_1_water-shortage-fever-dengue

[A map showing the location of Thiruvananthapuram in Kerala state can be accessed at http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thiruvananthapuram. A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map showing the location of Kerala state, can be accessed at http://healthmap.org/r/1dR5. - Mod.TY]

- Viet Nam (Ho Chi Minh City). 3 Jul 2012. 6 teams of medical inspectors have been set up to try to control dengue fever in HCM City, which has spread since the rainy season started in May. Nearly 250 cases of dengue fever were treated at hospitals in one week, according to the city's Health Department. Meanwhile, since early June, the number of cases of dengue fever totalled 3500, 9 per cent lower than last year [2011]; 4 of the patients died. Vo Minh Quang, from HCM City's Tropical Hospital, said on average, the hospital received 20 cases of dengue fever a day. Do Chau Viet, a doctor at Paediatrics Hospital No 2, said that since the beginning of the rainy season, the number of children hospitalised for dengue fever had risen.
http://vietnamnews.vnagency.com.vn/social-issues/226899/wet-brings-dengue-hand-foot-mouth.html

[A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map showing the location Ho Chi Minh City can be accessed at http://healthmap.org/r/008O. - Mod.TY]
